<div id="lae-posts-carousel-5cc1fdfe9bb7f" class="lae-posts-carousel lae-container" data-settings='{"arrows":true,"dots":false,"autoplay":false,"autoplay_speed":3000,"animation_speed":300,"pause_on_hover":true,"display_columns":3,"scroll_columns":3,"gutter":10,"tablet_width":800,"tablet_display_columns":2,"tablet_scroll_columns":2,"tablet_gutter":10,"mobile_width":480,"mobile_display_columns":1,"mobile_scroll_columns":1,"mobile_gutter":10}'><div data-id="id-149" class="lae-posts-carousel-item"><article id="post-149" class="post-6 page type-page status-publish hentry"><div class="lae-entry-text-wrap  nothumbnail"><h3 class="entry-title"><a href="https://www.zewschodu.com.pl/?p=149" title="Kak poluchit' Pol'skoe Grazhdanstvo?" rel="bookmark">Kak poluchit' Pol'skoe Grazhdanstvo?</a></h3><div class="lae-entry-meta"><span class="published"><abbr title="niedziela, Styczen, 2019, 12:38 pm">Styczen 13, 2019</abbr></span><span class="lae-terms"><a href="https://www.zewschodu.com.pl/?cat=10">Poleznaia informatsiia</a></span></div><div class="entry-summary">My pomozhem vam so vsemi formal'nostiami, neobkhodimymi dlia polucheniia grazhdanstva. Nashi spetsialisty ob'iasniat vam kak proiti vsiu protseduru. Poluchenie pol'skogo grazhdanstva - chto vy dolzhny znat'? Grazhdanstvo - eto postoiannaia iuridicheskaia sviaz' mezhdu fizicheskim litsom i stranoi. Na praktike eto oznachaet, chto grazhdanin dannoi strany imeet prava i obiazatel'stva pered gosudarstvom, a gosudarstvo po otnosheniiu [&hellip;]</div></div></article><!-- .hentry --></div><!-- .lae-posts-carousel-item --><div data-id="id-147" class="lae-posts-carousel-item"><article id="post-147" class="post-6 page type-page status-publish hentry"><div class="lae-entry-text-wrap  nothumbnail"><h3 class="entry-title"><a href="https://www.zewschodu.com.pl/?p=147" title="Kak poluchit' status rezidenta EU" rel="bookmark">Kak poluchit' status rezidenta EU</a></h3><div class="lae-entry-meta"><span class="published"><abbr title="niedziela, Styczen, 2019, 12:38 pm">Styczen 13, 2019</abbr></span><span class="lae-terms"><a href="https://www.zewschodu.com.pl/?cat=10">Poleznaia informatsiia</a></span></div><div class="entry-summary">Razreshenie na prozhivanie dolgosrochnogo rezidenta ES iavliaetsia razresheniem, kotoroe daet pravo na postoiannoe prozhivanie v Pol'she. Reshenie o vydache razresheniia na prozhivanie vydaetsia na neopredelennyi srok. Sam vid na zhitel'stvo deistvitelen 5 let, chto oznachaet, chto cherez 5 let vid nado obmeniat'. Na osnovanii razresheniia na prozhivanie dolgosrochnogo rezidenta ES, vydannogo v Pol'she, inostranets ne [&hellip;]</div></div></article><!-- .hentry --></div><!-- .lae-posts-carousel-item --><div data-id="id-145" class="lae-posts-carousel-item"><article id="post-145" class="post-6 page type-page status-publish hentry"><div class="lae-entry-text-wrap  nothumbnail"><h3 class="entry-title"><a href="https://www.zewschodu.com.pl/?p=145" title="Postoiannyi vid na zhitel'stvo" rel="bookmark">Postoiannyi vid na zhitel'stvo</a></h3><div class="lae-entry-meta"><span class="published"><abbr title="niedziela, Styczen, 2019, 12:37 pm">Styczen 13, 2019</abbr></span><span class="lae-terms"><a href="https://www.zewschodu.com.pl/?cat=10">Poleznaia informatsiia</a></span></div><div class="entry-summary">Reshenie o vydache razresheniia na postoiannoe prozhivanie (Pobyt staly) vydaetsia na neopredelennyi srok. Sam vid na zhitel'stvo deistvitelen 10 let, chto oznachaet, chto kazhdye 10 let nado meniat' plastikovuiu kartochku, a samo razreshenie na prebyvanie vydaetsia bessrochno. Na osnovanii razresheniia na postoiannoe prozhivanie, vydannogo v Pol'she, inostranets ne imeet prava rabotat' v drugoi strane. Razreshenie [&hellip;]</div></div></article><!-- .hentry --></div><!-- .lae-posts-carousel-item --><div data-id="id-143" class="lae-posts-carousel-item"><article id="post-143" class="post-6 page type-page status-publish hentry"><div class="lae-entry-text-wrap  nothumbnail"><h3 clas